To compile and install this program simply run:

./configure --with-platform=gnome && make       for a Gnome desktop, or
./configure --with-platform=maemo3 && make      for the Maemo 3 platform.

Scripts to generate Debian packages are provided as well, run

./build-gnome-package.sh         for a Debian GNU/Linux system, or
./build-maemo-package.sh         for Maemo 3
